Territory - Class in model
The Territory class represents, intuitively, a territory in the game of Risk, complete with name, owner, armies, continent, color, and list of adjacent territories.
Territory(String, Continent) - Constructor for class model.Territory
Constructs a new Territory so that name and continent are set to their respective parameters, numArmies is zero, and adjacent is set to an empty ArrayList.

Constructs a new Territory so that name, continent, and color are set to their respective parameters, numArmies is zero, and adjacent is set to an empty ArrayList.
